## 🚀 Project Overview

A professional capstone project focused on **Supply Chain & Logistics Data Analysis** using **Microsoft Excel**. This project transforms raw operational data into actionable business insights through dashboards, KPIs, pivot reports, and trend analysis.

It demonstrates how data-driven decisions can improve supplier performance, warehouse productivity, delivery efficiency, and cost control.

---

## 🎯 Business Objectives

✔ Analyze supplier reliability  
✔ Improve warehouse performance  
✔ Track order fulfillment rates  
✔ Reduce delivery delays  
✔ Monitor procurement costs  
✔ Support strategic decision-making  

---

## 📊 Key Insights Generated

### 📌 Supplier Performance
- Total orders vs delivered units  
- Supplier-wise efficiency ranking  
- Delay / shortage identification  

### 📌 Warehouse Analysis
- Orders processed by warehouse  
- Fastest warehouse comparison  
- Capacity & efficiency trends  

### 📌 Regional Demand Analysis
- Region-wise sales/orders  
- High demand zones  
- Delivery performance by region  

### 📌 Cost Optimization
- Total spend analysis  
- Cost per unit trends  
- High-cost supplier/category detection  

